}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== This device is sold as the '''[[Advantek Networks]]''' AWR-11N-RT. :[http://www.speedguide.net/routers/advantek-networks-awr-rt-11n-wireless-n-broadband-1565 On '''SpeedGuide.net'''] :[http://web.archive.org/web/20101211205905/http://advanteknetworks.com/support/awrrt11n/AWR-RT-11N.pdf Manual for the AWR-11N-RT via archive.org]
"G1700714100120", "V1.2", and "REV : B OSP" is silkscreened on the main board. :"G1700717000100" and "V1.0 GOLD 2T3R" is silkscreened on the top of the wireless module. "MINI-PCI TYPE IIIB" (R), "WLAN Card" (R), RT2820+RT2860" (L), and "REV:12(Module)" (L) is silkscreened on the sides of the card by contacts.
Default settings are per the manual for the AWR-11N-RT..
